Wallets

Suggest Edits

Cashfree supports a wide range of wallets to receive payments. The full list of supported wallets with the payment code is available below. These payment codes are useful to communicate with Cashfree when you have a customised payment flow and collect payments on your website or application directly. These codes will help us redirect you to the selected wallet.

Payment Code and Wallet Name

S. NoWallet NamePayment Code
1FreeCharge4001
2MobiKwik4002
3Ola Money4003
4Airtel Money4006
5Paytm4007
6Amazon Pay4008
7PhonePe4009

📘

  • By default FreeCharge, MobiKwik, Ola Money, and Airtel Money is activated for every payment gateway account.
  • Amazon Pay and PhonePe needs to be activated by Cashfree team for your payment gateway account. To get it enabled for your account reach out to Cashfree team at [email protected].
  • Paytm needs to be activated by Cashfree team for your payment gateway account. The reconciliation and refund APIs are not supported by Cashfree for Paytm. To get it enabled for your account reach out to Cashfree team at [email protected].
